## Ab MAAN LO LEADER CRASH HO GAYA
-----------------------------------

Leader Broker-1 par tha aur crash ho gaya.

Ab Kafka ko naya Leader elect karna hoga.

Question:

Kafka kisko naya Leader banaye?


## CASE 1: AGAR FOLLOWER-2 KO LEADER BANA DIYA JAYE
------------------------------------------------------------

Follower-2 ke paas sirf offset 3 tak ka data hai i.e

Offset 0 -> A
