1. TopicConfig.CLEANUP_POLICY_DELETE
2. TopicConfig.CLEANUP_POLICY_COMPACT


## TopicConfig.CLEANUP_POLICY_DELETE
-------------------------------------

Purpose:

-> Kafka ko batata hai ki cleanup ka method kya hoga.

Meaning:

-> Purana data delete karke cleanup karna hai.

Note:

-> Ye cleanup strategy hai.
-> Ye decide karta hai "cleanup kaise hoga".


## TopicConfig.RETENTION_MS_CONFIG
-------------------------------------

Purpose:

-> Kafka ko batata hai ki records kitne time tak retain karne hain.

Meaning:

-> Specified time complete hone ke baad purana eligible segments delete kiya ja sakta hai.

In This Example:

String.valueOf(7 * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000)

-> 7 Days

Meaning:

-> Records ko 7 din tak retain karo.
-> 7 din ke baad eligible segments delete kiye ja sakte hain.

Note:
-> Ye cleanup strategy nahi hai.



