## IDEMPOTENT PRODUCER :
------------------------

Consider the previous example where Consumer-1 publishes events to payment-topic.

In this scenario, Consumer-1 is acting as a Producer because it is producing messages to payment-topic.

## PROBLEM
-------------

Maan lo Consumer-1 publish karta hai:

