## OBSERVATION
----------------

Yahan:

✖ Consumer Crash nahi hua

✖ Offset Commit ka bhi koi issue nahi tha

Problem sirf Producer Retry ki wajah se hui.

Producer ko ACK nahi mila,
isliye usne same message dobara bhej diya.

Aur Broker ne usse ek naya message samajh kar
phir se store kar liya.

