payment-topic me duplicate event create ho gaya.


## SOLUTION
--------------

Isi Producer-Retry wale duplicate problem ko solve karne ke liye Kafka provide karta hai:

✔ Idempotent Producer

Idempotent Producer ensure karta hai ki Producer retries ki wajah se
same message broker par multiple baar store na ho.


## How Idempotent Producer is implemented
-------------------------------------------

Question:

Broker ko kaise pata chalega ki:

Payment-101

ek completely naya event hai

ya

Producer Retry ki wajah se dobara aaya hua wahi event hai?

