Isliye Kafka ek alag mechanism use karta hai.

## KAFKA INTERNALLY USE KARTA HAI:
---------------------------------
1: Producer ID (PID)
2: Sequence Number


1: PRODUCER ID (PID)
---------------------

Jab Producer Idempotency enable karta hai:

