to Kafka us Producer ko ek unique Producer ID assign karta hai.

Example:

Producer ID = 5001

Ab Kafka ko pata hai ki:

Ye saare messages Producer-5001 se aa rahe hain.

2: SEQUENCE NUMBER
-------------------

Kafka Producer har message ke saath ek sequence number bhi bhejta hai.

Example:

